26:15.000 --> 26:20.000
with the main approaches that are implemented in management.

26:20.000 --> 26:31.000
As for these approaches, they have been proposed a lot in the 200-year history of management development.

26:31.000 --> 26:38.000
But we will focus on those that have proven their effectiveness,

26:38.000 --> 26:44.000
their ability to organize and manage production,

26:44.000 --> 26:48.000
and which are used now, among other things.

26:48.000 --> 26:52.000
These are the approaches that are effective.

